what all of the fuss is about.

15:24.715 --> 15:27.760
Yeah, I guess.
Maybe.

15:27.760 --> 15:30.930
Is he gonna help you get some
in‐home care for your grandma?

15:30.930 --> 15:33.891
Well, yeah, he's gonna
straighten all that out.

15:33.933 --> 15:35.560
I mean, really, this was,
like, a perfect time

15:35.601 --> 15:36.769
for him to come home

15:36.811 --> 15:37.770
because, clearly,
I can't get it done.

15:37.770 --> 15:39.272
(Landry)
You know what, Matty?

15:39.313 --> 15:40.731
I think what he needs

15:40.773 --> 15:43.568
is to come and see...

15:43.609 --> 15:45.903
my new band,
Crucifictorious!

15:45.945 --> 15:48.865
Anyone?
Broken Spoke.

15:48.906 --> 15:50.950
This Friday
after the game.

15:50.950 --> 15:52.785
Doors open at 11:00‐‐you gotta
get there early, though.

15:52.785 --> 15:53.953
It's gonna be pretty packed.

15:53.995 --> 15:55.746
We have to go
to that, don't we?

15:55.788 --> 15:56.914
Well, if we don't go,

15:56.956 --> 15:59.000
I don't really think anyone
else is gonna be there, so‐‐

16:02.336 --> 16:03.921
[knock on door]

16:03.963 --> 16:05.006
Yep.

16:07.091 --> 16:08.467
Hi.

16:08.509 --> 16:09.927
Hey.

16:09.969 --> 16:12.889
[TV plays]

16:12.930 --> 16:14.640
Guess what I have.

16:14.640 --> 16:15.808
What?

16:15.808 --> 16:18.936
Dirty, dirty,

16:18.978 --> 16:20.605
dirty

16:20.646 --> 16:22.940
quad porn.

16:22.982 --> 16:24.483
What?

16:24.483 --> 16:25.985
(woman)
Before you engage

16:25.985 --> 16:28.321
in any sexual activity
with a partner,

16:28.321 --> 16:30.823
it will be helpful to know
how your new body works.

16:30.823 --> 16:33.951
This can most effectively
be done by masturbation.

16:33.993 --> 16:36.996
Listen, Lyla, can we just shut
this off and talk for a few‐‐
No.

16:37.038 --> 16:39.665
I know it's not exactly
the porn you were expecting,

16:39.707 --> 16:41.709
but there's some
useful stuff in here.

16:41.709 --> 16:42.668
Keeping an open mind

16:42.668 --> 16:45.504
and using your imagination
in the wheelchair

16:45.546 --> 16:48.633
can allow for spontaneity
and pleasure

16:48.674 --> 16:49.759
in sexual activity.

16:49.800 --> 16:50.843
Enjoy yourself.

16:50.885 --> 16:53.763
