to the hillside bank

22:42.903 --> 22:45.030
"and runs deep and green.

22:45.072 --> 22:47.533
"The water is warm, too,
for it has slipped twinkling

22:47.533 --> 22:49.118
"over the yellow sands
in the sunlight

22:49.159 --> 22:50.828
before reaching
the narrow pool."

22:50.870 --> 22:53.455
What did I just say
just now?

22:55.082 --> 22:57.376
I don't know‐‐some stuff
about a river.

22:57.418 --> 22:59.670
Okay, well, what did this
river look like?

22:59.712 --> 23:01.797
It's real pretty, Landry.

23:03.716 --> 23:05.384
Okay.

23:05.384 --> 23:07.469
