of the river"‐‐

23:07.511 --> 23:09.722
What the hell is Riggins
doin' in there?

23:09.722 --> 23:12.641
Studying.

23:15.102 --> 23:16.186
Hey, Dad.

23:16.228 --> 23:17.730
What, uh‐‐

23:17.771 --> 23:18.731
what are you doing?

23:18.772 --> 23:20.566
