driving me crazy.

23:20.608 --> 23:21.859
I had to get out
of the house.

23:21.901 --> 23:24.737
She can be a little much
sometimes.

23:24.737 --> 23:26.572
Why didn't you tell me
how bad it was?

23:26.572 --> 23:28.115
Well, it's not that bad‐‐
[alarm beeps]

23:29.783 --> 23:30.868
Grandma!

23:32.703 --> 23:33.829
Grandma!

23:35.122 --> 23:36.081
Grandma!
Huh?

23:36.123 --> 23:37.583
Grandma, you all right?

23:37.625 --> 23:38.542
You gotta be
kidding me.

23:38.584 --> 23:41.003
What did I tell you
about using the stove?

23:41.045 --> 23:43.756
What is wrong with you?
You're acting like a damn child!

23:43.756 --> 23:45.549
Dad, calm down.
It was an accident.

23:45.591 --> 23:47.676
I told you three times
to lay away from the stove!

23:47.718 --> 23:48.928
Dad, don't yell at her.
You're just gonna scare her.

23:48.969 --> 23:50.846
You okay?
No, no, no.
[sniffling]

23:50.888 --> 23:51.764
Don't cry, it's okay.

23:51.805 --> 23:53.432
