he said he never wanted to be.

25:27.735 --> 25:28.819
Exactly.

25:28.861 --> 25:30.154
I gotcha.
Exactly.

25:30.195 --> 25:32.031
Without Lennie, George
lost all his humanity.

25:32.031 --> 25:33.824
Yeah, that's messed up.

25:35.200 --> 25:37.036
